---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<BaseLayout title="Membership — Torquay Leander">

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="crumb">
      <a href={`${base}/`}>Home</a>
      <span>›</span>
      <span>Membership</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Membership</h1>
    <p>Join one of Devon's leading competitive swimming clubs. We offer flexible membership options to suit all commitment levels — with no minimum training hours required for squad selection.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="welcome">
  <div class="inner welcome-inner">
    <p class="label">Membership of Torquay Leander</p>
    <p class="welcome-text">As a club that has been around for many years, we have had many generations of the same family return to swim at Torquay Leander because we pride ourselves on being a friendly, approachable, fun yet competitive swimming club.</p>
    <p class="welcome-text">We rely on our volunteers — both coaches and parents — to do their bit wherever possible. Whether that is running the tuck shop, volunteering on the committee, helping poolside or selling raffle tickets, there is a job for everybody.</p>
    <p class="welcome-text">If you are interested in joining us as a swimmer and would like to arrange a free trial, please take a look at our membership fees and get in touch.</p>
    <a class="welcome-cta" href={`${base}/about/join/`}>
      Arrange a free trial
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mem-intro">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="label">Explore Membership</p>
    <div class="mem-cards">
      <a class="mem-card" href={`${base}/membership/costs/`}>
        <div class="mem-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/><path d="M9 10h6"/><path d="M9 14h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="mem-card-body">
          <h3>Membership Costs</h3>
          <p>View current annual and monthly fee structures for all age groups and squad levels.</p>
          <span class="mem-link">View costs →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="mem-card" href={`${base}/membership/benefits/`}>
        <div class="mem-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="mem-card-body">
          <h3>Membership Benefits</h3>
          <p>Discover what's included in your membership — coaching, competitions, kit and more.</p>
          <span class="mem-link">See benefits →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="mem-card" href={`${base}/about/join/`}>
        <div class="mem-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><line x1="19" y1="8" x2="19" y2="14"/><line x1="22" y1="11" x2="16" y2="11"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="mem-card-body">
          <h3>Join Us</h3>
          <p>Ready to get started? Find out how to register and book your free trial session.</p>
          <span class="mem-link">Join now →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how-it-works">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="label">How Membership Works</p>
    <div class="hiw-grid">
      <div class="hiw-card">
        <div class="hiw-num">1</div>
        <h3>Club &amp; Swim England membership</h3>
        <p>Every swimmer must be a member of both Torquay Leander and Swim England. We manage this for you — the annual club membership fee includes your Swim England registration, which provides insurance and allows you to compete.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-card">
        <div class="hiw-num">2</div>
        <h3>Annual fees due by 31 January</h3>
        <p>The annual membership fee is reviewed each year by the Finance Committee and is due by 31 January. Reduced rates apply for swimmers transferring from another club or joining later in the year.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-card">
        <div class="hiw-num">3</div>
        <h3>Monthly swimming fees by direct debit</h3>
        <p>Monthly subscriptions are based on the number of hours swum each week and are paid by direct debit through Club Organiser, set up when you join.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--black); padding: 64px 5vw 56px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-hero::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 60px;
    background: #fff; clip-path: polygon(0 100%, 100% 0, 100% 100%);
  }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .crumb { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: 0.78rem; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .crumb a { color: var(--red); text-decoration: none; }
  .crumb span { opacity: 0.5; }
  .page-hero h1 { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .page-hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.7; }

  .inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--red); margin-bottom: 18px; }

  .welcome { background: #fff; padding: 72px 5vw 56px; }
  .welcome-inner { max-width: 820px; }
  .welcome-text { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .welcome-cta {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px;
    background: var(--red); color: #fff; text-decoration: none;
    padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.92rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(220,38,38,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .welcome-cta:hover { background: var(--red-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .mem-intro { background: #f8fafc; padding: 64px 5vw; }
  .mem-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .mem-card {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 18px;
    background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 24px;
    text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .mem-card:hover { border-color: var(--red); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(220,38,38,0.1); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .mem-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 52px; height: 52px;
    background: var(--red-light); border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: var(--red);
  }
  .mem-card-body h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .mem-card-body p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .mem-link { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--red); }

  .how-it-works { background: #fff; padding: 64px 5vw 80px; }
  .hiw-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
  .hiw-card { border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 24px; }
  .hiw-num {
    width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 10px; background: var(--red); color: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .hiw-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text); }
  .hiw-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.86rem; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mem-cards, .hiw-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .welcome, .mem-intro, .how-it-works { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
  }
</style>
